{"article_id":"gkh90AJ6VIFPIyMQ","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"EL PASO , Texas -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"If Beto O'Rourke runs for president ,","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"he should thank President Donald Trump for the kick in the pants .","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"For three months , O ' Rourke had drifted in and out of public view ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"slipping slightly in public opinion polls","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"as he vacillated on a 2020 bid .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"But Trump ' s appearance in O ' Rourke ' s hometown on Monday night served to elevate the former Texas congressman as a potential rival .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"And","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"as Trump confronted O ' Rourke at a campaign-style rally on an issue central to both of their political identities","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"- immigration and the border wall -","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"O ' Rourke seized the opportunity","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"to re-establish his footing .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"\" Yeah , I ' m back in the mix around an issue","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"that could not be more important for our country and for our community , \"","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"he told","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"before addressing thousands of screaming supporters at a baseball field steps from the coliseum","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"where Trump was redoubling his call for a U.S.-Mexico border wall .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"To oppose Trump ' s agenda ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"O ' Rourke said ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"\" All of us right now have a responsibility","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"to do all","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"that we can ,","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"and this is me doing my best . \"","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"If O ' Rourke was testing Democrats ' appetite for his potential candidacy ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"the signs","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"he saw on Monday","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"were reaffirming","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"- beginning with a march to the rally","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that was so thick with supporters","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that organizers linked arms in a circle around O ' Rourke and his family","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"to keep them moving through the crowd .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Young Democrats rushed the line ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"wearing \" Viva Beto ! \" buttons","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"and hoisting \" Beto 2020 \" signs .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Chants of \" Beto , Beto \" echoed under freeway overpasses","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"as O ' Rourke and the throng passed through .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" You did good , El Paso ! \"","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"O ' Rourke said","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"when he arrived at the baseball field on a cold , windswept night .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" We have so much to give , so much","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"to show the rest of the country ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and we ' re doing it right now . \"","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"The speech","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"- and O ' Rourke ' s promotion of it beforehand -","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"marked a pivot for O ' Rourke from a contemplative period","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"of wayfaring","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"to a more traditional brand of campaign politics","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"following his closer-than-expected loss to Republican Ted Cruz in the Texas Senate race last year .","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Engaging the president on the wall ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"O ' Rourke did not retreat to his online journal","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"or livestream a conversation with his dental hygienist about life on the border ,","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"as he did last month .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"Nor did he break for the interstate for a soul-searching journey through the Southwest .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"Instead , O ' Rourke did what any Democrat","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"tilting toward a run for president","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"might do .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"He participated in a conference call with reporters Monday afternoon ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"before Trump arrived for his campaign rally here .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Then he timed his speech","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"to bracket Trump ' s appearance ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"ensuring side-by-side coverage .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"\" There ' s certain things","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"where you just can ' t go off in the desert and act like Job in the wilderness , \"","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"said New Hampshire attorney and Democratic activist Jay Surdukowski ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"who co-chaired Martin O ' Malley ' s 2016 presidential campaign in New Hampshire","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"and who traveled to El Paso for O ' Rourke ' s rally .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"\" You ' ve got to get real ,","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and he really is showing","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"he can turn it on","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"and get right back in the campaign mode . \"","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Trump was dismissive of O ' Rourke ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"mocking him as \" a young man","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"who ' s got very little going for himself","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"except he ' s got a great first name. \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"But even Republicans could appreciate O ' Rourke ' s deft political play .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Jeff Roe ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"who was Cruz ' s chief strategist ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"called his handling of Trump ' s visit a \" home run swing . \"","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"\" It shows","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"if he can find a balance","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"between being smart and strategic and a [ yin ] to the president ' s yang ,","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"that ' s what Democrats are seeking , \"","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"Roe said .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"\" When he ' s doing a bong tour through Southwest America ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"it ' s a little less invigorating to Democratic primary voters . \"","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"O ' Rourke told reporters Monday","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"that he did not interpret Trump ' s visit as a personal challenge ,","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"but rather as \" an effort","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"to use this community as a prop","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"to make his case for the border wall . \"","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"O ' Rourke has been criticizing the existing fencing along the border since","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"long before Trump turned the construction of a wall into a centerpiece of his 2016 campaign and , now , his bid for a second term .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Never before could O ' Rourke draw so much attention to the issue .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"\" All of a sudden , out of the blue , El Paso ' s gotten big on the national radar , \"","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"said Boyd Brown , a former South Carolina lawmaker and former Democratic National Committee member","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"now working on a \" Draft Beto \" campaign .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"The former Democratic congressman has said","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"he will decide whether to run for president by the end of the month ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"expressing lingering concerns about the effect","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"a campaign might have on his young family .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"Some rallygoers","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"yearning for a 2020 run","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"took it as a positive sign","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"that O ' Rourke was joined by his wife and children Monday ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"though they often accompany him to events .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"\" Oh , man , I get to be with and behind my community , \"","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"O ' Rourke said backstage , along the backstop of the baseball diamond .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"\" I love it ...","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"This is America ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"this is the border ,","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"this is El Paso .","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"It ' s all of those things at their best .","depth":13},{"id":113,"text":"It ' s so positive ,","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"there ' s no hate ,","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"there ' s nothing negative in the slightest about it . \"","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"Then O ' Rourke removed his jacket","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"and climbed onto a platform in the infield","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"to address the crowd .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"\" We are the example","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"that the United States of America needs right now , ''","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"he said to cheers .","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"`` This is where we make our stand ! \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":245,"left":0,"right":244,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":244,"left":124,"right":243,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":162,"right":242,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":162,"left":143,"right":161,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":126,"right":142,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":3,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":6,"right":141,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":141,"left":130,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":7,"right":129,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"